{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-28","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 28","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada, naučili ste kako da postavljate pitanja koristeći <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span> / <span class=\"highlighted-text\">does</span> i kreirate negativne rečenice korišćenjem <span class=\"highlighted-text\">don't</span> / <span class=\"highlighted-text\">doesn't</span>. Hajde da ponovimo. Zapamti:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Potvrda: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">He does work on weekends.</span> (to znači da osoba radi vikendom)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Hasi: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">He doesn't work on weekends.</span> (što znači da osoba ne radi vikendom)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Srpski: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Does he work on weekends?</span> (pita da li neko radi vikendom)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Pročitajte deo razgovora i popunite praznine koristeći <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">don't</span>.</p>\n</section>","explanation":null,"challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"English","superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","block":"learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","lang":"en-US","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-28"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>Tom: How about you? BLANK you have any hobbies?</p>\n<p>Sophie: That's cool. I like photography, but I BLANK think of it as a hobby.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"Do","feedback":"<p>Tom postavlja pitanje u vezi sa zabavom Sofije, koje zahteva <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span>.</p>"},{"answer":"don't","feedback":"<p>Sophie izjavljuje negativnu izjavu o tome da nešto ne treba uzimati za zabavu, što zahteva <span class=\"highlight